    <abstract>
      <t>This document deals with end-to-end cryptographically signed e-mail. It introduces a novel structure for signed e-mail that is designed to avoid creating any disturbance in legacy e-mail clients. This "unobtrusive" signature structure removes disincentives for signing e-mail.</t>
